{
  "stem": "1343.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And even more so, the Jewish forced labor parties because they had no proper clothing and they were exposed to the elements.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And every once in a while came the news that one or another had died and was buried there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was the last we heard of them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the Hungarians, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were digging [SIGHS] ditches for, I guess, tanks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were preparing for the Hungarian soldiers lodgings.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were taking care of horses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All kinds of manual jobs that the soldiers were saved from doing it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was called in '40, but he home after six months.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Almost 50.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is was-- so difficult to bear.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not only that he was taken away at that age, but he was physically already-- you know, in those days, a 50-year-old man was an old man.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In March, 1944, they came into Hungary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And within a month, with the help of the Hungarian Gendarme and police, rounded up the Jews and forced them into ghettos.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The atmosphere was already very tense.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Our-- my brothers were already in the camps, so we really lived under a lot of strain and stress and worry.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Life was not what it used to be, naturally.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we did-- In the early '40s and 41, we still had radios, and we listened to the BBC.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we knew more or less how the war proceeded.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were hoping that, first of all, America did not enter the war then yet, [INAUDIBLE] and the moment they entered, we thought that's it, now it will be finished.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Little did we know that it will still drag out for another three-- three and a half-- four years.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
